                &amp;&amp; this.yShape &gt; (y-DIST) &amp;&amp; this.yShape &lt; (y+DIST) 
                &amp;&amp; this.lengthShape &gt; (length-DIST) &amp;&amp; this.lengthShape &lt; (length+DIST))
        {
